name: Chapter 2: The Forest
description:
"You fled the maze in hopes of finding answers and freedom. Instead, you are now in a dense, humid forest where the sun is barely shining. There is a road... where will this road lead you? It is definitely a path that has already been used... But by whom? 

What will you find in the forest? are you going to get lost? or find your way to the answers you're looking for?"

----------------------------------------------

I hope you enjoy this interactive NFT. It was made for PC/Mac Browsers.

Don’t miss this 2nd chapter of a 3 part NFT point & click game :)

Have fun!!
